_sText:
Fyseb_italia - Beta 1
(just needs some massive cosmetic treatment as long as no bugs are found...)

Map doesn't really resemble much of Italy at all, but this it's what I named it when I started. 
So...eh...

Releasing this just to get GAMEPLAY feedback. The map's layout is done. Only thing that needs done is alot of cosmetics. 

Installation - 

Drag and drop the cstrike folder into

{LOCAL} / Program Files / Steam / Steamapps / {YOU} / Counter-Strike Source

Local being the drive that Steam is installed on, normally C:
You being your steam user id.

Map Things -

The doors in front of your spawn each teleport you to different areas of the map.
The door you choose also decides the weapons you get.

Door 1 gives you
(CT) - M4, (T) - Ak47, USP, 1 Flash, 1 HE

Door 2
M3, Deagle, 1 Smoke, and 1 HE

Door 3
(CT) - TMP, (T) - Mac10, p228, 2 Flashes

Door 4
Scout, USP, 2 Flashes

Door 5
m249, 5-7, 1 Smoke, and 1 HE
